    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Beastmaster Approach:</strong> 14th and 17th level</em></p>\n<p>When you enter your rage, you can choose up to 5 allies that you can see within 30 feet of you. You gain 5 temporary hit points for each creature. For the duration of your rage, once on each of their turns, an affected ally can add your rage damage bonus to a weapon attack's damage roll.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature five times. You gain an additional use at 17th level. You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
